          <h3>How can I contact BulldogClip?</h3>
          <p>Can't find the answer to your question here? <a href=<%= new_contact_path %> class="faq-link">Get in touch</a> and we will try our best to answer it.</p>
          <a class="top" href="#top">Back to top</a>
